Module net.etf.project
Package net.etf.project.model.vehicles

Class MalfunctionWrapper

java.lang.Object
net.etf.project.model.vehicles.MalfunctionWrapper
public class MalfunctionWrapper extends Object
This class serves as a wrapper for malfunction data to be displayed in a GUI table. It contains the type of vehicle, vehicle ID, description of the malfunction, and the date and time of the malfunction.
